casebody.data:
STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
William T. LIEPE, Defendant-Respondent. C-22 September Term 2018
080788 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 5, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004431-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the appellant may serve and file a supplemental brief on or before December 4, 2018, and respondent may serve and file a supplemental brief forty-five (45) days after the filing of appellant's supplemental submission, or, if appellant declines to file such a submission, on or before January 18, 2019.
